  <h1>Data Deletion Policy</h1>
  <p>We respect your privacy and your right to control your personal information.</p>
  
  <h2>How to request data deletion</h2>
  <p>If you would like us to delete your personal data from our systems, please contact us using one of the following methods:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:vyaw2003@gmail.com">vyaw2003@gmail.com</a></li>

  <h2>What happens after you request deletion</h2>
  <p>Once we receive your request, we will:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Confirm receipt of your request within 3 business days.</li>
    <li>Delete your personal data from our systems within 30 days.</li>
    <li>Notify you once the deletion has been completed.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Exceptions</h2>
  <p>Certain information may be retained if required by law or for legitimate business purposes (e.g., preventing fraud).</p>

  <p>For questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:vyaw2003@gmail.com">vyaw2003@gmail.com</a>.</p>
